metadata.name: Moonlight
metadata.description:
Moonlight

✤ ✤ ✤

This is the first piece of my "Her" collection. It's about love, about her, about us, about you and about time. It's about a journey, a visual story. She's a poppy. She's rooted in me.

"My eyes followed up the slope which, outside the hedge, rose steeply to the fields, a poppy that had strayed and been lost by its fellows"

✤ ✤ ✤

Artwork by Mannay (2022)
